title: Ingenuity highlights tomorrow's tech leaders (The University of Adelaide)
text: ( Source : The University of Adelaide ) Tuesday, 20 October 2015 The men and women who will shape Australia's technical innovation of the future will showcase their work at a free public event at the Adelaide Convention Centre next week.
